,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:32:33.000Z","msg":"我寧願唔儲錢。18-28 歲 嘅拍拖珍貴回憶。<br />\n<br />\n用錢都唔會買到果種快樂。<br />\n<br />\n旅行可以唔去，拖就一定要拍。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 連登仔那有女阿，你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263e29dabab311cf1c0d52db4f387e252b110a3b","tid":2340024,"uid":121076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916295f3d6ac8e2eca97fb434cd818ea0c6d94a3","tid":2340024,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"正常淨係家用都唔止3000<br />\n不過見佢最後拎哂d錢幫屋企人為債<br />\n無得咁計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"樓上話此post已完果幾個咪選擇性失明囉"},{"pid":"0767c2bdbbc4022874961badb2a619a84e104cca","tid":2340024,"uid":339231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60bb1e302af25d640082abd960877a69cb3b82ee","tid":2340024,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c77c45af4020c98eeb81556a5bbb1c18eb7aea2","tid":2340024,"uid":133977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗比家用<br />\n私樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"唔洗俾家用同有私樓 父母應該好識做人 唔係養兒防老 可惜生著個傻豬仔玩爛手牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"唔算玩爛啦，屋企有事拎到80萬出黎，幾多人有都未必肯拎啦"}]}